Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.71,0:13:09.19,inu-internal,KAZU,0,0,0,,{\a6}P-Píše oboma rukami?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.99,0:13:10.72,score-left-dark,TEXT,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,1)}Akiyama Shinobu
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.99,0:13:10.72,score-right-dark,TEXT,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,1)}Huzimaki Hotaru
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.18,0:13:13.98,inu-internal,KAZU,0,0,0,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.28,0:13:19.74,inu-main,HAMI,0,0,0,,Ešte stále nemôžem tú schopnosť používať príliš dlho.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.74,0:13:20.73,inu-internal,KAZU,0,0,0,,Tak ju nepoužívaj!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.92,0:13:22.90,inu-main,HAMI,0,0,0,,Ale nesmiem prehrať!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.56,0:13:25.99,inu-internal,KAZU,0,0,0,,Hamin zbesilý útok pokračuje.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.99,0:13:28.48,inu-internal,KAZU,0,0,0,,Tým, že hrotom pera udržuje stabilný rytmus,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.99,0:13:31.24,inu-internal,,0,0,0,,svojho súpera uspáva...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.56,0:13:35.00,inu-main,HAMI,0,0,0,,Písacia technika Osawi, \NWake Up Canceler!
